visibility: SANDBOX
license: OFL
category: serif
subsets: menu,latin,latin-ext

family: Quando

designer: Joana Correia da Silva

approved: true
description: <p>Quando is a serifed text typeface inspired by \
  brushy handwritten letters seen on an italian poster from the \
  second world war. Quando is a flexible text typeface made for \
  the web whose personality consistently shows in both small \
  and large sizes. Quando's low contrast design helps it work \
  better on screens and smaller sizes. Especially distinctive \
  letterforms include letters like the a, g, x and Q. Quando's \
  friendly feeling along with its clarity and familiarity \
  makes it suitable for a broad range of uses.</p>

font.Quando-Regular.ttf.style: normal
font.Quando-Regular.ttf.weight: 400

